- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper deals with developing models that can assist clinical decision making, which can be considered an application of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper uses sequence-to-sequence models, which are commonly used in natural language processing, and applies them to medical time series data. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses neural network models, specifically sequence-to-sequence models, to learn representations of medical time series data.
